content: I've been playing the ad-supported free versions of these games for years and immediately jumped on this ad-free collection. The added options in some of the games are greatly appreciated, as is the login option to transfer progress from the individual games to this collection. The amount of content on offer here is more than worth it.

Challenging but not impossible games, and the developer is actively adding features, such as help filling things in (thank you so much for that!) Please add highlighting numbers next (perhaps via long-press on the "pencil" button)
